		<title>一天上6次厕所被解雇  前员工控告亚马逊歧视</title>
		<link>https://atvnewsonline.com/world/22148/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[李毓琇]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 24 Aug 2021 15:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
